00063 static void engine_update(RenderEngine *engine, Main *bmain, Scene *scene)

00070     RNA_pointer_create(NULL, engine->type->ext.srna, engine, &ptr);

00134 static void rna_RenderEngine_unregister(Main *UNUSED(bmain), StructRNA *type)
00135 {
00136     RenderEngineType *et = RNA_struct_blender_type_get(type);
00137 
00138     if (!et)
00139         return;
00140     
00141     RNA_struct_free_extension(type, &et->ext);
00142     BLI_freelinkN(&R_engines, et);
00143     RNA_struct_free(&BLENDER_RNA, type);
00144 }
00145 
00146 static StructRNA *rna_RenderEngine_register(Main *bmain, ReportList *reports, void *data, const char *identifier,
00147                                             StructValidateFunc validate, StructCallbackFunc call, StructFreeFunc free)
00148 {
00149     RenderEngineType *et, dummyet = {NULL};
00150     RenderEngine dummyengine = {NULL};
00151     PointerRNA dummyptr;
00152     int have_function[4];
00153 
00154     /* setup dummy engine & engine type to store static properties in */
00155     dummyengine.type = &dummyet;
00156     RNA_pointer_create(NULL, &RNA_RenderEngine, &dummyengine, &dummyptr);
00157 
00158     /* validate the python class */
00159     if (validate(&dummyptr, data, have_function) != 0)
00160         return NULL;
00161 
00162     if (strlen(identifier) >= sizeof(dummyet.idname)) {
00163         BKE_reportf(reports, RPT_ERROR, "registering render engine class: '%s' is too long, maximum length is %d",
00164                     identifier, (int)sizeof(dummyet.idname));
00165         return NULL;
00166     }
00167 
00168     /* check if we have registered this engine type before, and remove it */
00169     for (et = R_engines.first; et; et = et->next) {
00170         if (strcmp(et->idname, dummyet.idname) == 0) {
00171             if (et->ext.srna)
00172                 rna_RenderEngine_unregister(bmain, et->ext.srna);
00173             break;
00174         }
00175     }
00176     
00177     /* create a new engine type */
00178     et = MEM_callocN(sizeof(RenderEngineType), "python render engine");
00179     memcpy(et, &dummyet, sizeof(dummyet));
00180 
00181     et->ext.srna = RNA_def_struct(&BLENDER_RNA, et->idname, "RenderEngine");
00182     et->ext.data = data;
00183     et->ext.call = call;
00184     et->ext.free = free;
00185     RNA_struct_blender_type_set(et->ext.srna, et);
00186 
00187     et->update = (have_function[0])? engine_update: NULL;
00188     et->render = (have_function[1])? engine_render: NULL;
00189     et->view_update = (have_function[2])? engine_view_update: NULL;
00190     et->view_draw = (have_function[3])? engine_view_draw: NULL;
00191 
00192     BLI_addtail(&R_engines, et);
00193 
00194     return et->ext.srna;
00195 }
